By bartamihii 1980s, THY lahaa filo ah 30 diyaarad. Waxa ay duulimaadkeedu ahayd saddex milyan oo rakaab ah sannadkiiba ilaa 16 dalxiis oo gudaha ah iyo saddex darsin oo caalami ah. Duulimaadyadu waxay ahayd sahayda ugu weyn ee Turkiga ah ee dalka debedda. Turkish Airlines waxay bilowday hawl-galka Airbus A310s 1985, taas oo u oggolaatay duulimaadyada Singapore in 1986. Waddada New York City via Brussels waxaa lagu daray 1988-kii.
























































































































































